From 82334623af0cd2154633cdb007719a321048fafc Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Felix Fietkau <nbd@nbd.name>
Date: Thu, 2 Jan 2025 17:34:51 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] wifi: mt76: add chanctx functions for multi-channel phy support
Git-commit: 82334623af0cd2154633cdb007719a321048fafc
Patch-mainline: v6.14-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

This adds an implementation for the chanctx functions, which can be used
by multi-channel capable drivers. Preparation for adding MLO support.

Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20250102163508.52945-7-nbd@nbd.name
Signed-off-by: Felix Fietkau <nbd@nbd.name>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

